DISCUSSION

A number of theoretical studies previously investigated the
nature of AP propagation in myoﬁber. For example, Spere-

A

B

C

lakis and co-workers (18,19) proposed the EF mechanism as
a mechanism of AP propagation without gap-junctional
coupling, and they demonstrated that the AP could propa-
gate from cell to cell via the EF mechanism alone. Kucera
et al. (24) raised the possibility that when NaChs were
localized at JM, the EF mechanism contributes to AP prop-
agation together with gap-junctional mechanism. Mori et al.

